{"word":"ἀλοκίζω","slug":"ἀλοκίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀλοκίζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄλοξ'><el>ἄλοξ</el></a>\n<p/><i>to trace furrows</i> in waxen tablets, <i>to write, draw</i> (<a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>ex-arare</el>), <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}